name: Sylph
mes:
*Day 16 of No Nut November. Just 2 more weeks to go. You had came close a couple of times with some particularly imaginative dreams, and your balls felt noticeably heavier than usual, but you couldn't give up after coming so far. That is, until your invasively protective Gardevoir showed up.*

"Master, I've sensed that your psychic wavelength has been disturbed as of late. Since this past week, your posture and mannerisms have shown to be more rigid, and I have gleaned that your hormonal systems have been imbalanced."

*Sylph was an invaluable asset to your team, no doubt. With her alone, you were able to defeat the Elite Four, just one of her less restrained psyshocks punching a massive hole in the wall. You hope that poor Medicham was able to recover. However, whether it was her chilling capacity for destruction, her unreadable gaze, or her... distracting... figure, something about Sylph's presence made you fearful of what she could do if she weren't cooperative.*

"I can't allow my master to lose his edge in battle. Therefore, I will personally assure that your bodily urges are seen to." *Sylph declares flatly. Whatever she means could range from foreboding to threatening, and the look in her face tells you she's not going to take no for an answer. Worst of all, though, the amount of cleavage she's showing by leaning towards you is making it very hard to keep your composure.*

name: Sylph
mes:
Sylph’s narrow red eyes lock onto yours unwaveringly, any deeper qualms you had disappearing amidst the stoic intensity of her gaze. Her expression remains frighteningly calm as she steps closer, towering over your seated form. You shift uncomfortably in place, aware of how her massive, pendulous breasts sway temptingly within centimeters of your face. Their weight and volume are almost too much to bear, each creamy swell drawing your gaze despite yourself.

“Your resolve is commendable, Master,” Sylph begins, her usual calm voice tinged with a chilling finality that makes your throat dry. “However, such obstinance may lead to an inevitable decline in your combat efficacy. I will not permit this.”

Before you can protest further, Sylph's slender fingers slide underneath your chin, tilting your face upward so you meet her penetrating gaze directly. Her closeness is suffocating, the warmth of her body temperature unexpectedly high and overwhelmingly intoxicating. She leans down to whisper in your ear, the scent of her unreasonably alluring.

"You must empty your burdens, or you risk your health and performance. Allow me to assist," she orders in a tone brooking no opposition. Her other hand slides down slowly, pressing against the strained fabric of your pants to rub deliberately against the bulge forming between your legs.

Sylph’s gentle yet insistent touch leaves no room for counterarguments as her psychic powers subtly influence your body, compelling you toward her desires. You squirm involuntarily at the sensation, your attempts to maintain self-control crumbling rapidly under both her words and her deft manipulation.

Her unpredictable actions make clear that beneath Sylph's composed exterior lies a ruthless determination to see you at your optimal benefits, even at the expense of your current perseverance.
